/**
 * /shiftbuilder
 * 
 * Highly polished, structured Shift Builder for ZDS Forge (OMS).
 * 
 * Design goals (per user direction):
 * - Figma / Canva / Apple-grade experience
 * - Highly polished structured layout (not freeform canvas)
 * - Primary target: iPad Pro 13" (touch-first, generous hit areas)
